text: Territoria enim hujus agelli ista sunt.
Primitus of alorriðe uppe on anne þoure.
Þanne þurh reowe on delesburg middenwearde.
Þane on wyrtruman þane on burg þanne on anne dich.
Þanen anlang ðies hagen oð anne þorn on hacggen hamme.
Þanen on anne hege ðat on irichte on anne oc ðonne est over melenbroc on anne<../images/tbar.gif>on anne stapel eft to anne alerriðe.
